{"type":null,"faqId":38958,"title":"手环不与手机绑定，可以单独使用么？","answer":"<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\n.p1{text-indent:0.29166666in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:0.25in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;}\n.p3{text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;}\n</style>\n<div>\n<p>\n</p>\n\"您好，手环首次使用时候必须与手机进行配对，从手机同步时间到手环。此时您可以使用手环看时间、监测运动/睡眠数据。但是来电提醒、信息提醒等时尚功能需要通过蓝牙连接手机且华为穿戴APP处于运行状态时才能使用哟。<br>\n建议您将APP加入到受保护的后台应用程序中，以避免APP被后台自动清除。以P7为例，选择“设置“—”受保护的后台应用“，找到华为穿戴APP打开右侧开关。\"\n<br>\n<p></p>\n</div>","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"4268","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1441673016000,"seriesProductName":"B0-Honor","visitedTimes":97,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"荣耀手环 zero,单独使用,不绑定手机","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}